Class ConfigureBakerPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.concordium.sdk.transactions.ConfigureBakerPayload

  • public class ConfigureBakerPayload
extends Object
    Payload for configuring a baker. The [Default] implementation produces an empty configure that will have no effects.
